name: Verfiy POST external Chat API /v1/chat/completions returns valid data
description:
### Pre-conditions:
- DeepSeek app installed.

### Steps:
- Login with valid credentials.
- POST `external` OpenAI Compatible Chat API `{hostname}/v1/chat/completions`.

### Verify that:

- API response matching expected json schema.

.venv/lib/python3.13/site-packages/aiohttp/resolver.py:126: in resolve
    raise OSError(None, msg) from exc
E   OSError: [Errno None] DNS server returned general failure

tests/reporting_hooks/reporting.py:49: in wrapper
    result = await func(*args, **kwargs)
             ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
tests/test_cases/steps/api_steps/api_steps.py:490: in verify_external_chat_api_completions

    async with self._session.post(

    self._resp: _RetType = await self._coro
                           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
.venv/lib/python3.13/site-packages/aiohttp/client.py:779: in _request
    resp = await handler(req)
           ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
.venv/lib/python3.13/site-packages/aiohttp/client.py:734: in _connect_and_send_request
    conn = await self._connector.connect(
.venv/lib/python3.13/site-packages/aiohttp/connector.py:672: in connect
    proto = await self._create_connection(req, traces, timeout)
            ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
.venv/lib/python3.13/site-packages/aiohttp/connector.py:1239: in _create_connection
    _, proto = await self._create_direct_connection(req, traces, timeout)
               ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
